v1
1: Download upto first 100 videos of all playlist in playlist.txt in playlist folder
2: Option to set quality for all videos of playlist

v1.1
Added option to download audio version of videos in mp3 format

v1.2
1: Videos will be downloaded one at a time so that download of single video is completed quickly and to avoid the load
2: Videos which are already downloaded wont get downloaded again to save bandwidth.

v2(Efficiency update)
1: Now any number of videos of particular playlist can be downloaded
2: Once current download completes then only other link will be fetched to reduce load on api
3: Cache implementation. Once the data is fetched from api, its response will be stored as cache thus making it more faster to access the previous data.
